---
import { CATEGORIES, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-border bg-bg-elevated">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="lg:col-span-1">
        <p class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-fg">{SITE_TITLE}</p>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-xs text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
          Segunda renda para quem trabalha de carteira assinada, sem aparecer, sem enrolacao.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-subtle uppercase">Categorias</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
          {CATEGORIES.map(({ name, slug }) => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/categoria/${slug}/`} class="text-sm text-muted no-underline transition-colors hover:text-accent">
                {name}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-subtle uppercase">Links</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
          <li><a href="/blog/" class="text-sm text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">Todos os artigos</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about/" class="text-sm text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">Sobre</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contato/" class="text-sm text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">Contato</a></li>
          <li><a href="/politica-de-privacidade/" class="text-sm text-muted no-underline hover:text-accent">Politica de Privacidade</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 border-t border-border-subtle pt-8 sm:flex-row">
      <p class="text-sm text-subtle">&copy; {year} {SITE_TITLE}. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-subtle">Conteudo educativo - resultados variam conforme dedicacao e contexto.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>